mbieland: Double Tap]]''<ref>{{cite tweet |user=Zombieland |number=1090345133319413760 |date=January 29, 2019 |title=#10YearChallenge? Challenge Accepted. #Zombieland2}}</ref>\n| Tallahassee\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/zombieland-2-plot-details-tease-zombies/|title=First Zombieland 2 Plot Details Tease New Zombies And More|website=We Got This Covered|author=Joseph, Matt|date=January 21, 2019|accessdate=January 21, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Midway (2019 film)|Midway]]''\n| [[Chester W. Nimitz|Admiral Chester Nimitz]]\n|\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Venom 2]]''\n| Cletus Kasady / [[Carnage (comics)|Carnage]]\n| Post-production\n|-\n| TBA\n| ''[[Kate (film)|Kate]]''\n|\n| Post-production\n|}\n\n===Television===\n<!-- Please note: do NOT use \"rowspans\" per WP:FILMOGRAPHY -->\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 1985\u20131993\n| ''[[Cheers]]''\n| [[Woody Boyd]]\n| 200 episodes\n|-\n| 1987\n| ''Bay Cove''\n| Slater\n| Television film\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1988\n| ''[[Mickey's 60th Birthday]]''\n| Woody Boyd\n| Television special\n|-\n| ''[[Killer Instinct (1988 film)|Killer Instinct]]''\n| Charlie Long\n| Television film\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1989\n| ''[[Dear John (American TV series)|Dear John]]''\n| Richard\n| Episode: \"Love and Marriage\"\n|-\n| ''[[Saturday Night Live]]''\n| Himself (host)\n| Episode: \"Woody Harrelson/[[David Byrne]]\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1990\n| ''[[Walt Disney anthology television series|Walt Disney's Wonderful World of Color]]''\n| Woody Boyd\n| Episode: \"Disneyland's 35th Anniversary Celebration\"\n|-\n| ''[[Mother Goose Rock 'n' Rhyme]]''\n| Lou the Lamb\n| Television film\n|-\n| 1992\n| ''Saturday Night Live''\n| Himself (host)\n| Episode: \"Woody Harrelson/[[Vanessa L. Williams]]\"\n|-\n| 1994\n| ''[[The Simpsons]]''\n| Woody Boyd (voice)\n| Episode: \"[[Fear of Flying (The Simpsons)|Fear of Flying]]\"\n|-\n| 1996\n| ''[[Spin City]]''\n| Tommy Dugan\n| Episode: \"Meet Tommy