on]]\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" | 2008\n| ''[[Semi-Pro]]''\n| Ed Monix\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Sleepwalking (film)|Sleepwalking]]''\n| Randall\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Transsiberian (film)|Transsiberian]]''\n| Roy\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Surfer, Dude]]''\n| Jack Mayweather\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Management (film)|Management]]''\n| Jango\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Seven Pounds]]''\n| Ezra Turner\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2009\n| ''[[The Messenger (2009 film)|The Messenger]]''\n| Captain Anthony \"Tony\" Stone\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Defendor]]''\n| Arthur Poppington / Defendor\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Zombieland]]''\n| Tallahassee\n|\n|-\n| ''[[2012 (film)|2012]]''\n| Charlie Frost\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Bunraku (film)|Bunraku]]''\n| The Bartender\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2011\n| ''[[Friends with Benefits (film)|Friends with Benefits]]''\n| Tommy Bollinger\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Ethos (film)|Ethos]]''\n| Narrator (voice)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Rampart (film)|Rampart]]''\n| David Douglas \"Dave\" Brown\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2012\n| ''[[The Hunger Games (film)|The Hunger Games]]''\n| [[Haymitch Abernathy]]\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Seven Psychopaths]]''\n| Charlie Costello\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" | 2013\n| ''[[How to Make Money Selling Drugs]]''\n| Himself\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Now You See Me (film)|Now You See Me]]''\n| Merritt McKinney\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Out of the Furnace]]''\n| Harlan DeGroat\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Free Birds]]''\n| Jake (voice)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Hunger Games: Catching Fire]]''\n| rowspan=\"3\" | Haymitch Abernathy\n|\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[The Hunger Games: Mockingjay \u2013 Part 1]]''\n|\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[The Hunger Games: Mockingjay \u2013 Part 2]]''\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" | 2016\n| ''[[Triple 9]]''\n| Sergeant Detective Jeffrey Allen\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | ''[[Now You See Me 2]]''\n| Merritt McKinney\n|\n|-\n| Chase McKinney\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Duel (2016 film)|The Duel]]''\n| Abraham Brant\n|\n|-\n| ''[[LBJ (film)|LBJ]]''\n| [[Lyndon B. Johnson]]\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Edge of Seventeen]]''\n| Max Bruner\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" | 2017\n| ''[[Lost in London]]''\n| Himself\